# Luvimestra App Architecture

This Flutter app follows a simple architecture with the following key principles:

1. Use `setState` for state management - avoid complex state management libraries
2. Use `shared_preferences` for local data storage
3. No `freezed` package or `part` syntax allowed
4. No local image assets - all images should be loaded from URLs
5. No `cached_network_image` package - use standard network image loading
6. No account functionality implementation
7. No external fonts - use system fonts only

## Core Files Structure
- `main.dart` - App entry point, theme setup, and global configuration
- `app.dart` - Main app framework with bottom navigation and page switching

## Pages
- `realities_page.dart` - Parallel realities card list view
- `chat_page.dart` - Chat interface with AI characters
- `encounter_page.dart` - Tarot cards and astrology readings
- `radio_page.dart` - Radio stations list
- `radio_player_page.dart` - Radio player interface
- `settings_page.dart` - User settings and preferences

## Models
- `models/reality_model.dart` - Parallel reality character model
- `models/tarot_model.dart` - Tarot card and astrology model
- `models/radio_model.dart` - Radio station model

## Utils
- `utils/ai_service.dart` - AI chat and analysis service
- `utils/shared_prefs.dart` - Shared preferences wrapper
- `utils/navigation.dart` - Navigation helper functions